{"tid":1893610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個偽黃","createTime":"2020-02-23T11:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T19:01:21.000Z","uid":211549,"like":16,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee24d762846ec30ac4ca1f629c3766869e6bd46f","tid":1893610,"uid":211549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"同好多連登仔一樣<br />\n我都係由6月9號開始關注件事<br />\n其實我完全唔理解點解要反政府<br />\n但為咗打卡 我差唔多去齊曬啲遊行集會<br />\n當然每次都係到此一遊就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後hashtag翻香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n我平時返學會用老人卡 <br />\n我朋友以為我係因為不滿黨鐵<br />\n其實我係因為平先用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我鍾意食m記 日日食<br />\n平靚正<br />\n26蚊餐香港邊🐭有 仲有乜好反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我醒目啊 經過黃店嗰陣會打翻張卡<br />\n佢哋真係以為我係食咗先打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時印嘢會落樓下間影印鋪印<br />\n好似藍店黎<br />\n不過勝在夠近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通真係為咗黃藍行咁遠水路咩<br />\n彩你都痴線！<br />\n<br />\n講咗出黎已經舒服曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：全部虛構<br />\n偽黃死全家"},{"pid":"2fc0e5f47ec01d75e7cde6d22420ae754ca4f521","tid":1893610,"uid":211549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"舒服曬 又可以繼續做偽黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e59d568e50193a5ae9ef37631fe926f16e9e3dc","tid":1893610,"uid":224570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"d 低能仔真係以為我係不滿先跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14044d6fb7e2f2c95af2a7ec26b18ef9787fdca","tid":1893610,"uid":211549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e59d568e50193a5ae9ef37631fe926f16e9e3dc","tid":1893610,"uid":224570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20